    <section_number>8</section_number>
    <catch_line>Negligence In Maintaining Ferry</catch_line>
    <order_by>8</order_by>
    <text>
        A town which neglects to maintain a ferry as provided in the two preceding sections shall forfeit not more than one hundred dollars for each month such neglect continues.
    </text>
